<P>
NEWBURY PARK WINS IN SOFTBALL PLAYOFFS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Newbury Park High's Lea Lopez threw a two-hitter and had two hits to lead the 
visiting Panthers past Santa Maria, 3-0, in the quarterfinals of the Southern 
Section 5-A Division softball playoffs Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
Newbury Park (24-7) will meet Fountain Valley, a 3-2 winner over Lakewood St. 
Joseph, in the semifinals. Melody Bolger was two for four for Newbury Park, 
which extended a 1-0 lead with two runs in the sixth inning. 
</P>
</TEXT>
