BUSH, GEORGE; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN 
POLICY; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- CHINA; UNITED STATES -- POLITICS 
