the way the brain functions in interpreting a visual image. ; Photo, (Southland 
Edition A1) COMPUTER WHIZ: David Harris, 17, above, explains his entry in this 
year's State Science Fair for high school students, a sophisticated computer 
game called "Robowar." KEN LUBAS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
