<TEXT>
<P>
The 32nd annual Garden Grove Strawberry Festival begins today, highlighted by 
the slicing of the world's largest strawberry shortcake. 
</P>
<P>
The festival, which includes carnival games and rides, arts and crafts, and 
food and game booths, will get under way at 1 p.m. in Village Green Park, 12762 
Euclid Ave. 
</P>
<P>
The festival's main event, the Strawberry Festival Parade, will begin at 10:30 
a.m. Saturday. 
