<P>
DUTCH VOLLEYBALL TEAM TO PLAY AT UC IRVINE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Dutch women's team Dynamo will play the International Ambassadors in the 
Flo Hyman memorial volleyball match Thursday at the Bren Center at UC Irvine. 
</P>
<P>
The international team features several local players, including Rita Crocket 
of Newport Beach, a 1984 Olympian; Stella Berkabile of Westminster and Belinda 
Hilleary of Laguna Hills. The match will start at 7:30 p.m. 
</P>
