CAMPBELL SOUP PLANS SELLOFF OF SEVERAL EUROPEAN FOOD UNITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
CAMDEN, N.J. 
</P>
