<P>
The memories came rushing back Thursday when CBS anchorman Dan Rather visited 
the red-brick elementary school he attended in Houston. 
</P>
<P>
Rather was reunited with Alberta Taylor, 78, the second-grade teacher whom he 
credits with teaching him to read. 
</P>
